b'Days':
b'For longer than she can remember, the monster Azami has been alone. Time passes her by, and she merely watches. Her loneliness finally ends when she gains a family. Yet human lives are fleeting, and Azami may have no choice but to face an unbearable tomorrow where she is alone once again.
